snippet.description:

I
作詞・作曲：藤原基央
編曲：BUMP OF CHICKEN


時間がない　ここは命の瞬きの中だ
重なったら離れてしまう
ああ　伝えなくては　何をだったっけ
それじゃ思い出そう　今日　僕らで

これだけ大切なのに　
どうやれば　ちゃんと正しく大切にできる
ああ　一度だけでいい　本当の本当が見たいよ
みんなシャボン玉　瞬きの中

渡せない痛みの生まれた場所
そこにいるんだろ　聴こえてしまった
ひび割れながら鮮やかなままの
脈打つ記憶で作られた　始まりの声

さあ　やっと見つけた
ここまで来た　もう触れるよ
集めて　しまっておいた　勇気の全部で
君の生きる　その前にいる


あらゆる種も仕掛けも　使い果たした後の
諦めを許さない呪い
ああ　とても強く　長い間握っていた
願い事　世界をくれた魔法

乾かない雨を　白昼の夜を
ずっと連れてきたんだろ　そうして出会えた
未だ身体は息をする　痛みに血を巡らせる
その意味を知りたがるように

呼び合う今
鼓動の答え合わせができる
何を取り返したいの　一人じゃないぜ
僕も生きる　そのための夜


言葉は限界を超えて砕けた
網膜は君を確かに捉える
思い出そう　ありがとう
きっとこの時を待っていた


さあ　やっと見つけた
ここまで来た　もう触れるよ
傷付けたとしても　勇気の全部で
君と生きる

呼び合う今
鼓動の答え合わせができる
何を取り返したいの　一人じゃないぜ
僕も生きる　君と生きる　そのためにいる

snippet.title: [Official Trailer] มีสติหน่อยคุณธีร์ Me and Thee #MeAndTheeSeries
snippet.description:
“ธีร์ ธีรกิต เคียน ลี” ( ปอนด์ ณราวิชญ์ ) ลูกชายคนโตของมาเฟียเก่า ละทิ้งอดีตที่เคยค้าอาวุธมาทำธุรกิจน้ำหอมและเครื่องประดับแบรนด์อาเซนี่ แต่ดันเกิดเรื่องราวสุดวุ่นวายขึ้น เมื่อคุณธีร์ชอบ “อารัญ” ( แซนต้า พงศภัค ) นายแบบคนสนิทของ “พีช พีชยรัตน์” ( ภูวินทร์ ตั้งศักดิ์ยืน ) ช่างภาพฟรีแลนซ์ชื่อดังที่มาถ่ายแบบให้กับน้ำหอมคอลเลกชั่นใหม่ครั้งนี้ จากเป็นคนที่มีความสุขกับการอยู่เงียบๆ ใช้ชีวิต introvert แต่กำลังจะถูกทำลายไปตลอดกาลเพราะว่าต้องเป็นอาจารย์สอนวิชาจีบให้กับคุณธีร์ แต่กลับโดนจีบเองแบบเล่นใหญ่ ราวกับอยากสร้างประวัติศาสตร์หน้าใหม่แห่งการจีบบนโลกนี้

เรื่องราวความรักที่ทำให้พีชอยากจะตะโกนว่ามีสติหน่อยคุณธีร์! จะเป็นอย่างไร ติดตามได้ใน “มีสติหน่อยคุณธีร์ Me and Thee” ทุกวันเสาร์ เวลา 20:30 น. ทางช่อง GMM25 และดูออนไลน์ เวลา 21:30 น. บนแอป iQIYI และเว็บ iQ.com ที่เดียวเท่านั้น เริ่ม 15 พฤศจิกายนนี้

กำกับซีรีส์ : ณัฐพงษ์ มงคลสวัสดิ์

รายชื่อนักแสดง
ปอนด์ ณราวิชญ์ เลิศรัตน์โกสุมภ์  รับบท  ธีร์
ภูวินทร์ ตั้งศักดิ์ยืน            รับบท  พีช
เอส ศุภ สง่าวรวงศ์            รับบท  โมกข์
บอนนี่ ภัทราภัสร์ โบรัชตะสุวรรณ์  รับบท  ลูกพลับ
เพิร์ธ ธนพนธ์ สุขุมพันธนาสาร         รับบท  ตะวัน
แซนต้า พงศภัค อุดมโภชน์   รับบท  อารัญ

snippet.title: Animal Crossing: New Horizons – Nintendo Switch 2 Edition & Free Update – Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The Animal Crossing: New Horizons – Nintendo Switch 2 Edition game and a free update to the base game launch January 15, 2026. Only on the Nintendo Switch 2 and Nintendo Switch systems. Pre-orders are coming soon! Learn more: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/animal-crossing-new-horizons-nintendo-switch-2-edition-upgrade-pack-switch-2/?utm_source=DLC&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=S1017-01&utm_id=S1017-01
  
With enhanced resolution, mouse controls using the Joy-Con 2 controller, expanded online play*, and more features exclusive to Nintendo Switch 2, players can get even more out of the island life in Animal Crossing: New Horizons – Nintendo Switch 2 Edition! 
  
Plus, a free update is coming to Animal Crossing: New Horizons for players on both Nintendo Switch 2 and Nintendo Switch to enjoy. The free update includes a new resort hotel, additional amiibo** functionality, collaboration items, updates to online play, and more. 
  
We can't wait for you to see everything new on the island January 15, 2026! 
  
Nintendo Switch 2 players who already have Animal Crossing: New Horizons on Nintendo Switch can upgrade to the Nintendo Switch 2 Edition by purchasing the upgrade pack***. 
  
*Nintendo Switch Online membership (sold separately) and Nintendo Account required for online features. Membership auto-renews after initial term at the then-current price unless canceled. Not available in all countries. Internet access required for online features. Terms apply. nintendo.com/purchase-terms/ 
  
**amiibo sold separately. Visit amiibo.com for details on amiibo functionality. 
  
***Full version of Animal Crossing: New Horizons game required to use this content. Sold separately. For details, visit support.nintendo.com/switch2/upgradepack 

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://ninten.do/6008Spp2s

Request from hololive Productions to underage viewers

https://hololivepro.com/en/request-to-minors/
＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝
================================
RULES FOR CHAT (PLEASE READ THEM)

1. Be decent.

2. Let’s keep it light as much as we can!

3. If you TALK IN ALL CAPS LIKE THIS for anything that isn’t a quick reaction, a short phrase, etc. or an obvious joke you will be hidden from the channel and it is extremely difficult to undo. This is especially for advice/backseating.

4. I often welcome tips and have no issue getting advice/critique from chat. What matters is how you express it. If it’s worded as an insult or overtly demeaning remark, you will be banned by the mods. 
LIGHTHEARTED RIBBING AND TEASING IS OKAY.

Examples of OK backseating: “Try going in this direction.” “If you press this button, you can do 〇〇.” “Using that move isn’t effective.” “You’ll do better if you 〇〇.” “Get good.” = ALL OF THESE ARE OK. Yes, even the last one. But expressing your advice rudely doesn’t contribute to a good time for any of us. If you are getting frustrated watching the gameplay, take a break from the stream. 

5. Do not express anger or negativity towards any of the other girls, it’s unacceptable and you’ll be banned immediately. 

6. Spamming of any kind/repeating the same messages and phrases will result in a ban.

7. Feel free to chat in your language, but I won’t be able to read phrases I don’t understand out loud.

Let's have fun, skeletons!
==================================

snippet.title: UPSIDE DOWN (A Hazbin Hotel Song) - Black Gryph0n & Baasik
snippet.description:
STREAM #UPSIDEDOWN ON SPOTIFY: https://open.spotify.com/track/70lG2bwQd9OIaoIWbg0eMH?si=lZ7PDIkTR_Gwuf_9o-wa0A&nd=1&_branch_match_id=link-1512788054174522531

AND EVERYWHERE ELSE: https://ffm.to/bgb-upsidedown

Official Karaoke Track on BAASIK'S channel! https://youtu.be/wpg7k-Mwf_A?si=TFfCLJGqD4UGthyr

MORE ORIGINAL MUSIC HERE: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PrMjrvz5hyc&list=PLv1P-6YxEm6AgF6yiKtydFevNQV4RxKn4&index=1

OMG I can't believe we did ANOTHER Hazbin Hotel song! I thought we were done after Daisies, but Nate and I got to talking about the new season and Alastor's backstory and we had this idea... we just had to make a song about it!
Then Lux came in with her genius visual storytelling, and that was that! I hope y'all like it! It's one of my new faves!

CREDITS:


Written by Gabe & Nate brown (Black Gryph0n & Baasik)

Produced by Nate Brown (Baasik): https://www.youtube.com/user/Baasikmusic

Performed by Gabriel Brown (Black Gryph0n): https://www.youtube.com/c/BlackGryph0n

Animated by Luximus: https://youtube.com/@Luximus17?si=xzByJGFs_3R5mcpa (https://youtube.com/@Luximus17?si=xzByJGFs_3R5mcpa)



-- --- ---- ----- Lyrics ----- ---- --- --


“With your smile, turn the world upside down”

Sit down, I’m gonna tell ya
A little story ‘bout a sad little fella
He was a Dapper-Dan Cinderella
Oh, and lemme tell ya
It made the other fellas jealous

They made him cry
“Na na na”
Spit in his eye
“Ha ha ha”
How could they pick on such a friendly little guy?

This town was kinda broken
Not the kind of place you’d leave your doors open
Full of backwards, back-woods broke-men
Still he was copin’
Yeah he was dreamin’ hopin’

He’d get away
“Na na na”
Maybe someday
“Ha ha ha”
But on the radio his momma used to play.

“When it feels like all the world is wearing a frown
Put a smile on and spread it around.”

With your smile, turn the world upside down.

CHORUS:
Da da, da da da da
Da da da da da dada

Well now he had the spirit
And he would smile every time he’d hear it
Soon he knew every single lyric
Oh, and he would sing it
And in his sleep he’d dream it

All day and night
“Na na na”
Through every fight
“La La La”
You wouldn’t judge him if you knew what it was like

And how, as luck would have it
He got rewarded for his weird new habit
He earned a fat green stack of cabbage
And he planned to stash it
Till he was livin’ lavish

That fateful day
“Na na na”
He ran away
“La La La”
And he could hear the song his momma used to play

“When it feels like all the world is wearing a frown
Put a smile on and spread it around…”

With his smile, he’d turn the world upside down!

Chorus:
Da da, da da da da
Da da da da da dada

When it feels like all the world is wearing a frown
Put a smile on and spread it around.

With my smile, I turned the world upside down.


- -- --- ---- ----- END ----- ---- --- -- -

Hello DDR’s (dedicated description readers)

You guys, we have been going NON-STOP but it's all GOOD (except for yesterday, that was kinda scary) but everything else is good! Lots of new music, but we can't show you yet because it's all in stuff that we don't own... but hopefully we'll be able to show you soon!

Anyway, yesterday I went to Eugene to test-fly an airplane and had a complete loss of coms. Had to squawk 7600 and make my way to the runway via light-signal (first time for everything). Turns out the alternator was off and the battery died. The landing was also less-than-pretty and the wheel fairings were a bit too tight, so when we touched down, they sorta exploded. They had to shut down the runway and do a FOD walk to pick up the chunks of fiberglass! There were firetrucks and everything (fortunately, not necessary). Not my favorite test flight, but a good story!

Oh yeah, we recorded some new stuff for Billie Bust Up and guys... this game is going to blow your socks off. I really don't think I can overstate it. I can't WAIT for this game to come out!

OK, that's all I have time for. My wife is eepy but also wants to watch a movie, so I gotta go do that before she falls asleep and I have to carry her to bed. My back only has a few more of those trips left in it...

LOVE Y'ALL!!

~Gabe

snippet.title: Ek Deewane Ki Deewaniyat Mera Hua x Kabhi Jo Badal Barse Mashup | Aftermorning  | Saiyaara | Shreya
snippet.description:
A heartfelt blend of timeless romance and modern soundscapes — Ek Deewane Ki Deewaniyat Mera Hua brings together two beautiful worlds through emotion, melody, and passion.
 
More Aftermorning Viral Mashups : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLNSv8z24EefMuPV1lMnw28k5qN341cccz
Subscribe http://bit.ly/aftermorningmusic
Instagram https://www.instagram.com/aftermorningproductions/

Ek Deewane Ki Deewaniyat Mera Hua Mashup | Aftermorning | Harshvardhan | Shreya Ghoshal 
Remix  by : Aftermorning 
Mix Master: Vishal Rajput
Video Edit: Somnath Roy ( Afterlife Visual)
Release : AIDC
Music Production & Other work enquiries: yesugadeabhishek@gmail.com


Mera Hua
Shaam dhalti hai, aur main sochta hoon,
Tere bina bhi, main tujhmein kho jaata hoon.
Kuch lamhe the — adhure, kuch sapne the — pure,
Par har dafa tu tha, mere dil ke aas-paas zarur.
Yaad hai wo pal, jab tu muskurayi thi,
Waqt ruk gaya tha, khud zindagi sharmaayi thi.
Mujhe laga bas, ab kuch aur na chahiye,
Us ek pal ne, mujhe poora kar diya tha.
Tu door hai, par har subah tere saath uthta hoon,
Khidki se aane waali roshni mein tujhe dhoondhta hoon.
Tere bina bhi, tu mere saath hai,
Har saans mein tera ehsaas hai.
Kabhi socha nahi tha, pyaar itna chupke se aayega,
Zakhmon ko choo kar, dawa ban jaayega.
Tere jaane ke baad bhi, tu yahaan reh gaya,
Khali kamron mein, tera nasha mehka gaya.
Main likhta hoon, toh lafz tera roop le lete hain,
Gungunata hoon, toh sur tera naam keh dete hain.
Har silsilay ka anjaam tu ban gaya,
Main sirf tera tha… aur tu mera hua.
Kahin duaon mein, kahin armaanon mein,
Tu likha gaya hai meri kahani ke har gumaanon mein.
Aur chahe duniya keh de ye pyaar bewajah,
Mujhe toh bas itna kehna hai —
Tu mera sapna nahi… mera sach hua.
Tu mera hua.
